room_title: Escape room "A Night in the Fashion Store" by That Escape Room in San Francisco
room_description: A night shift guard reported to his boss that some supernatural activities are happening in the store every midnight. But the boss is currently traveling with his girlfriend. The guard was reported as missing after that night. It's now at 11 pm. You guys have one hour to find where the guard is, or what he left and get out of there.
